25:08.437 --> 25:34.714
Lately with the resurgence of the Vietnam War and 
all of the films that were showing how the Vietnam

25:08.437 --> 25:34.714
War veteran was so maligned and mistreated, Burn 
on the Fourth of July, Platoon,

25:08.437 --> 25:34.714
Hamburger Hill, whatever these movies were, I 
think It's also made young people today more aware

25:34.981 --> 26:01.512
of what a screwed up war that was and how we really 
had no place over there and even the soldiers came

25:34.981 --> 26:01.512
to believe it so that young men getting ready to go 
off to the Mideast today are probably going to cast

25:34.981 --> 26:01.512
a pretty jaundiced eye towards an American 
involvement in a place that really doesn't or who

25:34.981 --> 26:01.512
they feel we really shouldn't be. And I don't think 
they will just be very content to peacefully march

26:02.977 --> 26:09.587
around and say, hell no, we won't go. I think that's 
why the government's not so quick to push it. And

26:14.053 --> 26:22.886
also the parents now of many of those people in the 
60s have young sons and daughters who would be

26:14.053 --> 26:22.886
required to go. And I think the government knows

26:23.366 --> 26:28.714
that... The parents wouldn't support that. I 
don't think people in my generation, I have a

26:33.587 --> 26:37.092
17-year-old son, I don't want him to go. I would 
advise him not to go. And

26:39.295 --> 26:55.596
even parents, fathers or mothers who were over in 
Vietnam know or came to realize that that was

26:39.295 --> 26:55.596
really a war

26:58.529 --> 27:01.234
that Americans should have stayed out of. And they 
probably wouldn't want their sons over there. So

27:05.963 --> 27:17.044
either the government's going to have to come up 
with another real sneaky thing like Pearl Harbor

27:05.963 --> 27:17.044
to incite American support over there, which is 
really a scary but not unbelievable thought.

27:19.471 --> 27:22.321
or they're not going to have the support they need 
for that war. So I think we should all be thinking

27:22.341 --> 27:28.924
right now, what are they going to do to incite us to 
want to go over there?

